query:
SELECT c.name, COUNT(pc.productId) as product_count
FROM categories c
LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON c.id = pc.categoryId
WHERE c.name IN ('HPLC Columns', 'GC Columns', 'Guard Columns', 'SPE Cartridges', 'Filtration', 'Chromatography Supplies')
GROUP BY c.id, c.name
ORDER BY product_count DESC
